<LP>
   WASHINGTON -- MCI Communications Corp. named Daniel F.
Akerson and Richard T. Liebhaber to new posts of executive
vice president and group executive, effective immediately.
   Both men report to Bert C. Roberts, president and chief
operating officer.
</LP>
<TEXT>
