   The respective notes will mature on May 31, 1992, and Aug.
15, 1995.
   Tenders for the two-year notes, available in minimum
$5,000 denominations, must be received by 1 p.m. EDT
Wednesday at the Treasury or at Federal Reserve banks or
branches. Tenders for the five-year, two-month notes,
available in minimum $1,000 denominations, must be received
by 1 p.m. EDT Thursday.
